# Install dependencies
poetry install

# Activate virtual environment
poetry shell
```

### Code Quality Tools

```bash
# Format code with Black
poetry run black milombok_lib/

# Lint with Ruff
poetry run ruff check milombok_lib/

# Type checking with mypy
poetry run mypy milombok_lib/
```

